data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Country charmer! This beautiful 3 bed, 3 1/2 bath home is nestled in the trees in a park like setting and conveniently located in the heart of Greenbrier! Spacious floor plan! Large, open kitchen leads to separate sitting room/dining area with fireplace. Large pantry with lots of storage! Walk-in closets in bedrooms. Basement with half bath and 2 car garage! Enjoy the views from your large covered deck or covered front porch!
